Text: FW Jeffrey Skilling Loan were the only things missing from this draw which we received today Original Message From Irene Hargy Sent Wednesday May AM To Fernando Parra Cc Shelly Lambert Subject Jeffrey Skilling Loan Have received a draw request on the above and have ordered the inspection however we will need the following items prior to funding Borrowers signature on the page draw request Borrowers signature on the Contractors Disbursement Disclosure Borrowers signature on Change order Please forward to my attention Thanks Irene Hargy Ext CONFIDENTIALITY NOTICE The information contained in this ELECTRONIC MAIL transmission is confidential It may also be privileged work product or proprietary information This information is intended for the exclusive use of the addressees If you are not the intended recipient you are hereby notified that any use disclosure dissemination distribution other than to the addressees copying or taking of any action because of this information is strictly prohibited
